				<td colspan="2"><span>Ok, i've read everything I can on this.  I've tried ti myself over and over again recently on cougars or dire wolves in Iceclad (i'm level 30 right now.. almost 31).
<br />

<br />
No matter what I do, I always end up getting my butt handed to me and have to run to the zone :(
<br />

<br />
Anyone out there skilled in this who can take some time and explain, in detail, exactly how this is done? Also can you indicate exactly how your charm bank is set up and maybe a good place to PRACTICE this?
<br />

<br />
I know i'm asking a lot, but swarm kiting is supposedly so good, and it sounds FUN.. but so far i'm still much better of chant-kiting.  It may take me 5 minutes to kill something (ug), but at least I never get smacked into the ground.</span></td>
