				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Swarm Kiting, Please help :(<a name="2046"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 14 02 9:26 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey, maybe i can help. First and most important is ti NOT get any aggro from any of the mobs!!!! To do this, just either get close enough to pull mob or let it hit you, then let that mob attract others by running close to them. Get as many as you want, im comfortable with 8. Target 1 of them and charm, If you have no aggro, the others will all attack your pet. Watch the pets health. When it gets low I prefer to click my hide button which removes the charm effect. Then just dot and run that 1 til its dead. Lead others away from corpse then charm next 1, Again they will all attack, go loot first and watch health, low hide dot kill repeat till all gone. I hope this helped.
<br />

<br />
 <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-14.gif" border="0" alt="Devil" hspace="2" />Licorice Jellibeanz
<br />
52nd Minstrell of Tallon Zek</span></td>
